      <title>南非维持利率不变，政策制定者暗示将转向鸽派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/south-africa-central-bank-holds-rates-citing-inflation-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非央行在分歧意见中维持利率不变，六名决策者中有两名赞成降息，这可能预示着最早在 9 月份就会转向宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/south-africa-central-bank-holds-rates-citing-inflation-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:07:38 GMT</pubDate>
